Amelia M. WETZORK, Administratrix of the Estate of Frederick F. Wetzork, Deceased, v. READING COMPANY, Appellant. No. 9406. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit. Argued Nov. 4, 1947. Decided Nov. 20, 1947. Henry R. Heebner, of Philadelphia, Pa. (Wm. Clarke- Mason, of Philadelphia, Pa., on the brief), for appellant. B. Nathaniel Richter, of Philadelphia, Pa. (Richter, Lord & Farage, of Philadelphia, Pa., on the brief), for appellee.

Before BIGGS, GOODRICH and Mc-LAUGHLIN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the court below is affirmed.
